creator: Qboxus Technologies
descriptionHtml: Tankhaw is  safe, and easy-to-use employee attendance app. You can use it as an attendance app or register and keep a tab of your employees' attendance and work-shifts. You can also use it as a salary book and record employee payroll and maintain effective advance payment management.
descriptionShort: Application for staff attendance, work, Jobs & Salary Book.
title: Tankhaw - Attendance & Payroll

creator: Qboxus Technologies
descriptionHtml:
Pakistan’s Best Salary & Khata App for staff attendance, work, Jobs & Salary Book.

Tankhaw is a free employee management, work & salary management app, where you can easily manage all your Staff Salary And Attendance. Tankhaw offers a very easy to use and simple mobile app for payroll and employee management. Payments, advances and loan payment can also manage in this app.

Tankhaw is a 100% free, safe, and easy-to-use attendance management app. Tankhaw allows business owners or managers to track their employee’s check-in & check-out time and also keep a tab of your employees's work-shifts. Tankhaw is also providing a Smart RFID attendance management solution

Best and easiest solution for employee management. It’s the ideal app for every businesses, offices, daily labour management, worker & staff management. It can also be used to record employee payroll (salary or Tankhaw) and maintain effective advance payment management. Tankhaw replaces your traditional ledger account book.

Easiest Employee Management App

• Manage Staff attendance, verify staff presence in office or on-site location
• Auto track punch-in punch-out timing
• Track total working hours
• Employee’s salary & payroll software integration
• Calculate staff overtime and salary
• Auto deduct the leave, advance & early payment
• Calculate payout for pay per task employees
• Manage employee’s attendance and salary from anywhere on any device
• Tankhaw staff management app is available for every device and platform
• Ideal for the HR, admins, managers or business owners to manage employees and staffs on payroll
• Cashbook feature made easy for business owners, admins to manage their employees and staffs


Staff Attendance by Tankhaw:
Mark Attendance in one click. Tankhaw smartly calculates your staff's salary based on attendance inputs considering Overtime, Late Fine, Leaves, and Holidays.

Tankhaw issues early salaries to employees based on number of days worked and Salary amount. Instant salary advance & personal loan app.

You can manage Daily wage, Monthly wage and Work basis staff all at one place, in the Tankhaw App.
 
Send sms & WhatsApp notification to employees and staff using Tankhaw about payments, bonuses, daily work, attendance & leaves.
